            brand to new heights of perfection!
        </p>
      </div>
</div> 


<div class=" w-full h-auto ">
    <div class="flex text-xl items-center justify-between px-12 py-14">
        <h1 class=" font-glancyrRegular text-8xl" > SERVICES </h1> 
        <div>
            <Image src={world} class="h-28 w-28" alt=""/>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class=" h-auto px-12 mb-10">
    <div class=" bg-border-white h-[1px]">
    </div>
</div>


<div class="h-auto px-10 pb-10 sm:px-20 sm:pb-0 flex flex-col ">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row h-auto mb-10 sm:mb-96  ">
        <div class="sm:w-2/5 h-full z-0  ">
            <Image class="max-w-[800px] w-full  " src={animate2} alt=""/>
        </div>
        <div class=" sm:w-3/5 flex sm:flex-col gap-3 justify-center items-center ">
            <div class="flex gap-14 text-center ">
                <h1 class=" text-right sm:w-1/3 font-glancyrRegular sm:text-3xl">
                    IMPAULSIVE WEB DEVELOPMENT
                </h1>
                  <p class="text-left sm:w-2/3 font-glancyrThin text-xs mb-4 sm:mb-8 sm:text-2xl box-shadow6 ">
                    Combining unique design and rich technology we build 
