                    simplifications which makes us <span class=" text-neon-green">STAND OUT!</span>
                  </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-14 text-center ">
                <h1 class=" text-right sm:w-1/3 font-glancyrRegular sm:text-base">
                    AREAS
                </h1>
                  <p class="text-left sm:w-2/3 font-glancyrThin text-xs mb-4 sm:mb-8 sm:text-2xl box-shadow6 ">
                    Combining unique design and rich technology we build 
                    digital products exactly as they were designed, without shortcuts or any
                    simplifications which makes us <span class=" text-neon-green">STAND OUT!</span>
                  </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        
    </div>

</div>



<style>
     .gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(312.07deg, #B3E823 -35.99%, #FCE1E1 82.9%, #FFFFFF 172.6%);
